module-build: Module::Build (Build and install Perl modules)
module-build:
module-build: "Module::Build" is a system for building, testing, and
module-build: installing Perl modules. It is meant to be an
module-build: alternative to "ExtUtils::MakeMaker". Developers may
module-build: alter the behavior of the module through subclassing in
module-build: a much more straightforward way than with "MakeMaker".
